summary: AN ORDINANCE submitting to the voters by Charter referendum, Ordinance No. 98017 relating to and levying an excise tax in accordance with RCW 35.95 for the support of the public transportation system of the City; providing for certification to the Director of Department of Records and Elections of King County of the referendum proposition for ratification or rejection at the general municipal election to be held November 4, 1969 and prescribing the ballot title therefor.
